    "result": {"data":{"allStrapiBooks":{"nodes":[{"slug":"wulixuejiangyi","title":"费恩曼物理学讲义 1-3","author":"费恩曼(R.P.Feynman)","description":"本书为量子力学，系美国著名物理学家为本科生所作的演讲。本书共分三卷，第一卷包括力学、相对论、光学、气体分子运动理论、热力学、波等。第二卷主要是电磁学，第三卷为量子力学。","rank":50,"published_at":"2022-01-18T16:50:29.000Z","image":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#580808","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/5cbb6d38bb8883018fe15f7fb2a81ed8/3212f/_3bb1d0f981.jpg","srcSet":"/static/5cbb6d38bb8883018fe15f7fb2a81ed8/5c809/_3bb1d0f981.jpg 25w,\n/static/5cbb6d38bb8883018fe15f7fb2a81ed8/5c9f3/_3bb1d0f981.jpg 50w,\n/static/5cbb6d38bb8883018fe15f7fb2a81ed8/3212f/_3bb1d0f981.jpg 100w,\n/static/5cbb6d38bb8883018fe15f7fb2a81ed8/291ee/_3bb1d0f981.jpg 200w","sizes":"(min-width: 100px) 100px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/5cbb6d38bb8883018fe15f7fb2a81ed8/7f5c9/_3bb1d0f981.webp 25w,\n/static/5cbb6d38bb8883018fe15f7fb2a81ed8/de8f1/_3bb1d0f981.webp 50w,\n/static/5cbb6d38bb8883018fe15f7fb2a81ed8/fd5fd/_3bb1d0f981.webp 100w,\n/static/5cbb6d38bb8883018fe15f7fb2a81ed8/436db/_3bb1d0f981.webp 200w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 100px) 100px, 100vw"}]},"width":100,"height":140}}}}},{"slug":"qtdkj","title":"囚徒的困境","author":"[美] 威廉·庞德斯通","description":"本书用简明易懂的方式阐明了博弈论，是一部真正具有独创性的作品，体现在它以丰富的史料，开阔的视野和合乎逻辑的分析，以生动和直率的方式向读者讲述了冷战的历史，核时代的策略游戏和冯·诺伊曼的生平。揭露了战后令人毛骨悚然的一些政府间的尔虞我诈，是一本关于博弈论及其在冷战和核军备竞赛中的作用的出色的社会历史教科书。","rank":50,"published_at":"2022-01-18T14:26:21.000Z","image":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#080808","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/d019061b86200208a6c1f9c9dece3ce7/3212f/_57e871e3d1.jpg","srcSet":"/static/d019061b86200208a6c1f9c9dece3ce7/5c809/_57e871e3d1.jpg 25w,\n/static/d019061b86200208a6c1f9c9dece3ce7/5c9f3/_57e871e3d1.jpg 50w,\n/static/d019061b86200208a6c1f9c9dece3ce7/3212f/_57e871e3d1.jpg 100w,\n/static/d019061b86200208a6c1f9c9dece3ce7/291ee/_57e871e3d1.jpg 200w","sizes":"(min-width: 100px) 100px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/d019061b86200208a6c1f9c9dece3ce7/7f5c9/_57e871e3d1.webp 25w,\n/static/d019061b86200208a6c1f9c9dece3ce7/de8f1/_57e871e3d1.webp 50w,\n/static/d019061b86200208a6c1f9c9dece3ce7/fd5fd/_57e871e3d1.webp 100w,\n/static/d019061b86200208a6c1f9c9dece3ce7/436db/_57e871e3d1.webp 200w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 100px) 100px, 100vw"}]},"width":100,"height":140}}}}},{"slug":"game-theory","title":"博弈论","author":"朱·弗登博格 / 让·梯若尔","description":"博弈领域的两位领军人物的集大成之作，囊括了迄今为止除演化博弈之外的所有博弈论的理论和方法、代表了博弈论发展的最高水平。它不仅涵盖了博弈论的方方面面。而且几乎对每一个论题都给出了严密的数学推导和证明。","rank":50,"published_at":"2022-01-18T14:22:29.000Z","image":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#f81818","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/c3e6c26b5adbe7c7726a0d45c3503e0e/3212f/_daed3bcc0c.jpg","srcSet":"/static/c3e6c26b5adbe7c7726a0d45c3503e0e/5c809/_daed3bcc0c.jpg 25w,\n/static/c3e6c26b5adbe7c7726a0d45c3503e0e/5c9f3/_daed3bcc0c.jpg 50w,\n/static/c3e6c26b5adbe7c7726a0d45c3503e0e/3212f/_daed3bcc0c.jpg 100w,\n/static/c3e6c26b5adbe7c7726a0d45c3503e0e/291ee/_daed3bcc0c.jpg 200w","sizes":"(min-width: 100px) 100px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/c3e6c26b5adbe7c7726a0d45c3503e0e/7f5c9/_daed3bcc0c.webp 25w,\n/static/c3e6c26b5adbe7c7726a0d45c3503e0e/de8f1/_daed3bcc0c.webp 50w,\n/static/c3e6c26b5adbe7c7726a0d45c3503e0e/fd5fd/_daed3bcc0c.webp 100w,\n/static/c3e6c26b5adbe7c7726a0d45c3503e0e/436db/_daed3bcc0c.webp 200w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 100px) 100px, 100vw"}]},"width":100,"height":140}}}}},{"slug":"geb","title":"哥德尔、艾舍尔、巴赫","author":"[美] 侯世达","description":"集异璧－GEB，是数学家哥德尔、版画家艾舍尔、音乐家巴赫三个名字的前缀。《哥德尔、艾舍尔、巴赫书：集异璧之大成》是在英语世界中有极高评价的科普著作，曾获得普利策非小说奖。它通过对哥德尔的数理逻辑，艾舍尔的版画和巴赫的音乐三者的综合阐述，引人入胜地介绍了数理逻辑 学、可计算理 论、人工智能学、语言学、遗传学、音乐、绘画的理论等方面，构思精巧、含义深刻、视野广阔、富于哲学韵味。\n","rank":50,"published_at":"2022-01-17T08:22:33.000Z","image":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#080808","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/0d6164d5b24edb5e1673aa47be6f7079/3212f/_605fb608f7.jpg","srcSet":"/static/0d6164d5b24edb5e1673aa47be6f7079/5c809/_605fb608f7.jpg 25w,\n/static/0d6164d5b24edb5e1673aa47be6f7079/5c9f3/_605fb608f7.jpg 50w,\n/static/0d6164d5b24edb5e1673aa47be6f7079/3212f/_605fb608f7.jpg 100w,\n/static/0d6164d5b24edb5e1673aa47be6f7079/291ee/_605fb608f7.jpg 200w","sizes":"(min-width: 100px) 100px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/0d6164d5b24edb5e1673aa47be6f7079/7f5c9/_605fb608f7.webp 25w,\n/static/0d6164d5b24edb5e1673aa47be6f7079/de8f1/_605fb608f7.webp 50w,\n/static/0d6164d5b24edb5e1673aa47be6f7079/fd5fd/_605fb608f7.webp 100w,\n/static/0d6164d5b24edb5e1673aa47be6f7079/436db/_605fb608f7.webp 200w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 100px) 100px, 100vw"}]},"width":100,"height":140}}}}},{"slug":"zbzw","title":"众病之王","author":"[美] 悉达多·穆克吉","description":"一部饱含人文主义色彩的社科文化著作。作者悉达多•穆克吉历时六年，凭借翔实的历史资料、专业文献、媒体报道、患者专访等众多信息，向读者阐述了癌症的起源与发展，人类对抗癌症、预防癌症的斗争史。作者借由医学、文化、社会、政治等视角透露出一种社会化关怀；生动、文学性的写作手法展现出鲜活的人物和历史事件，让读者为之动容。","rank":50,"published_at":"2022-01-17T08:05:25.000Z","image":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#f8f8f8","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/490391663add7b6ff7f251e52fa50d16/3212f/_8b87e15cc6.jpg","srcSet":"/static/490391663add7b6ff7f251e52fa50d16/5c809/_8b87e15cc6.jpg 25w,\n/static/490391663add7b6ff7f251e52fa50d16/5c9f3/_8b87e15cc6.jpg 50w,\n/static/490391663add7b6ff7f251e52fa50d16/3212f/_8b87e15cc6.jpg 100w,\n/static/490391663add7b6ff7f251e52fa50d16/291ee/_8b87e15cc6.jpg 200w","sizes":"(min-width: 100px) 100px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/490391663add7b6ff7f251e52fa50d16/7f5c9/_8b87e15cc6.webp 25w,\n/static/490391663add7b6ff7f251e52fa50d16/de8f1/_8b87e15cc6.webp 50w,\n/static/490391663add7b6ff7f251e52fa50d16/fd5fd/_8b87e15cc6.webp 100w,\n/static/490391663add7b6ff7f251e52fa50d16/436db/_8b87e15cc6.webp 200w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 100px) 100px, 100vw"}]},"width":100,"height":140}}}}},{"slug":"swgwsm","title":"十万个为什么（第六版）","author":"韩启德 / 李大潜 / 沈文庆 / 吴启迪","description":"经过数百位编委、作者和编辑历时3年的辛勤努力，《十万个为什么》第六版以全新的问题、全新的体系、全新的内容、全新的样式问世。110多位中国科学院和中国工程院的院士担任编委，20多位中国一流科学家担纲分卷主编和副主编，具体负责组织相关分卷编纂工作，40多位院士亲自撰稿。同时还有来自世界各地、各个学科的700多位优秀科学家和科普作家参与了《十万个为什么》第六版的编写。全书包括600万字，7000余幅图片，共18分卷16开本的全彩色图文本。\n","rank":50,"published_at":"2022-01-17T08:02:37.000Z","image":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#f8f8f8","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/3b1a4420f9a3db967035b8647fdbd481/2c0b0/_5a7352d903.png","srcSet":"/static/3b1a4420f9a3db967035b8647fdbd481/ca013/_5a7352d903.png 25w,\n/static/3b1a4420f9a3db967035b8647fdbd481/8aaac/_5a7352d903.png 50w,\n/static/3b1a4420f9a3db967035b8647fdbd481/2c0b0/_5a7352d903.png 100w,\n/static/3b1a4420f9a3db967035b8647fdbd481/70f4f/_5a7352d903.png 200w","sizes":"(min-width: 100px) 100px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/3b1a4420f9a3db967035b8647fdbd481/7f5c9/_5a7352d903.webp 25w,\n/static/3b1a4420f9a3db967035b8647fdbd481/de8f1/_5a7352d903.webp 50w,\n/static/3b1a4420f9a3db967035b8647fdbd481/fd5fd/_5a7352d903.webp 100w,\n/static/3b1a4420f9a3db967035b8647fdbd481/436db/_5a7352d903.webp 200w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 100px) 100px, 100vw"}]},"width":100,"height":140}}}}},{"slug":"bianma","title":"编码","author":"[美] Charles Petzold","description":"本书讲述的是计算机工作原理。作者用丰富的想象和清晰的笔墨将看似繁杂的理论阐述得通俗易懂，你丝毫不会感到枯燥和生硬。更重要的是，你会因此而获得对计算机工作原理较深刻的理解。这种理解不是抽象层面上的，而是具有一定深度的。","rank":50,"published_at":"2022-01-17T07:52:19.000Z","image":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#f8f8f8","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/db90fa1a4021c2573ea793aa1a53fdd1/3212f/_8f98c096c1.jpg","srcSet":"/static/db90fa1a4021c2573ea793aa1a53fdd1/5c809/_8f98c096c1.jpg 25w,\n/static/db90fa1a4021c2573ea793aa1a53fdd1/5c9f3/_8f98c096c1.jpg 50w,\n/static/db90fa1a4021c2573ea793aa1a53fdd1/3212f/_8f98c096c1.jpg 100w,\n/static/db90fa1a4021c2573ea793aa1a53fdd1/291ee/_8f98c096c1.jpg 200w","sizes":"(min-width: 100px) 100px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/db90fa1a4021c2573ea793aa1a53fdd1/7f5c9/_8f98c096c1.webp 25w,\n/static/db90fa1a4021c2573ea793aa1a53fdd1/de8f1/_8f98c096c1.webp 50w,\n/static/db90fa1a4021c2573ea793aa1a53fdd1/fd5fd/_8f98c096c1.webp 100w,\n/static/db90fa1a4021c2573ea793aa1a53fdd1/436db/_8f98c096c1.webp 200w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 100px) 100px, 100vw"}]},"width":100,"height":140}}}}},{"slug":"smssx","title":"什么是数学","author":"R•柯朗 / H•罗宾 / I·斯图尔特","description":"本书是世界著名的数学科普读物，它搜集了许多经典的数学珍品，对整个数学领域中的基本概念与方法，做了精深而生动的阐述。无论是数学专业人士，或是愿意作数学思考者都可以阅读本书。特别对中学数学教师、大学生和高中生，本书是一本极好的参考书。","rank":50,"published_at":"2022-01-17T07:49:33.000Z","image":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#f8f8f8","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/f4255c86ca659d21f9efc2ea602637dc/3212f/_34e51c9a49.jpg","srcSet":"/static/f4255c86ca659d21f9efc2ea602637dc/5c809/_34e51c9a49.jpg 25w,\n/static/f4255c86ca659d21f9efc2ea602637dc/5c9f3/_34e51c9a49.jpg 50w,\n/static/f4255c86ca659d21f9efc2ea602637dc/3212f/_34e51c9a49.jpg 100w,\n/static/f4255c86ca659d21f9efc2ea602637dc/291ee/_34e51c9a49.jpg 200w","sizes":"(min-width: 100px) 100px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/f4255c86ca659d21f9efc2ea602637dc/7f5c9/_34e51c9a49.webp 25w,\n/static/f4255c86ca659d21f9efc2ea602637dc/de8f1/_34e51c9a49.webp 50w,\n/static/f4255c86ca659d21f9efc2ea602637dc/fd5fd/_34e51c9a49.webp 100w,\n/static/f4255c86ca659d21f9efc2ea602637dc/436db/_34e51c9a49.webp 200w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 100px) 100px, 100vw"}]},"width":100,"height":140}}}}},{"slug":"fmddl","title":"费马大定理","author":"[英] 西蒙﹒辛格","description":"西蒙・辛格（Simon Singh）出生于萨默塞特耶，具有印度旁遮普血统，曾在伦敦帝国学院学习物理，并在剑桥大学获得粒子物理学博士学位。在BBC电视台《明日世界》工作5年后，于1996年为《地平线》系列节目合作制作和导演了关于费马大定理的获奖记录片。","rank":50,"published_at":"2022-01-17T07:46:27.000Z","image":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#f8f8f8","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/f6fca50d4b6cfd75a167404229eeadd4/3212f/_fe1c6c1b28.jpg","srcSet":"/static/f6fca50d4b6cfd75a167404229eeadd4/5c809/_fe1c6c1b28.jpg 25w,\n/static/f6fca50d4b6cfd75a167404229eeadd4/5c9f3/_fe1c6c1b28.jpg 50w,\n/static/f6fca50d4b6cfd75a167404229eeadd4/3212f/_fe1c6c1b28.jpg 100w,\n/static/f6fca50d4b6cfd75a167404229eeadd4/291ee/_fe1c6c1b28.jpg 200w","sizes":"(min-width: 100px) 100px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/f6fca50d4b6cfd75a167404229eeadd4/7f5c9/_fe1c6c1b28.webp 25w,\n/static/f6fca50d4b6cfd75a167404229eeadd4/de8f1/_fe1c6c1b28.webp 50w,\n/static/f6fca50d4b6cfd75a167404229eeadd4/fd5fd/_fe1c6c1b28.webp 100w,\n/static/f6fca50d4b6cfd75a167404229eeadd4/436db/_fe1c6c1b28.webp 200w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 100px) 100px, 100vw"}]},"width":100,"height":140}}}}},{"slug":"daykx","title":"打开一颗心","author":"[英] 斯蒂芬·韦斯塔比","description":"“我经手过12000颗心脏。”作者在心外科暨胸外科从业数十年，手术成绩卓著。本书即汇集了作者经历的一些经典案例（多数发生在1970年代至2000年代之间），也剖白了作者的心路历程。\n\n工薪家庭的穷小子，被幼年时的医学纪录片鼓舞，也被亲人的离世刺痛，终于将自己历练成一名杰出的心外科医生。他为面试的成功而激动地徜徉在伦敦河岸街头，为先天心脏病或气道重度灼伤的小儿开胸，为病人和家属的焦灼与渴望而奋战，为对抗次日手术的焦虑而深入沙特沙漠欣赏夜空，为尽力修补而果断切削垂危的心脏，为救命而与医务主任对抗、“擅自”为病人安装人工的“电池”心，在命悬一线的攻坚手术面前还能讲出冷笑话……一位艺业精湛、傲气十足又敬畏生命的外科医生形象跃然纸上。那些十几年甚至几十年前就存在的顶尖外科技术也令读者叹为观止。\n","rank":50,"published_at":"2022-01-17T07:43:15.000Z","image":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#980808","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/bb138af500febb9eb3bbcdb8a39fcce2/3212f/_2748ab1763.jpg","srcSet":"/static/bb138af500febb9eb3bbcdb8a39fcce2/5c809/_2748ab1763.jpg 25w,\n/static/bb138af500febb9eb3bbcdb8a39fcce2/5c9f3/_2748ab1763.jpg 50w,\n/static/bb138af500febb9eb3bbcdb8a39fcce2/3212f/_2748ab1763.jpg 100w,\n/static/bb138af500febb9eb3bbcdb8a39fcce2/291ee/_2748ab1763.jpg 200w","sizes":"(min-width: 100px) 100px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/bb138af500febb9eb3bbcdb8a39fcce2/7f5c9/_2748ab1763.webp 25w,\n/static/bb138af500febb9eb3bbcdb8a39fcce2/de8f1/_2748ab1763.webp 50w,\n/static/bb138af500febb9eb3bbcdb8a39fcce2/fd5fd/_2748ab1763.webp 100w,\n/static/bb138af500febb9eb3bbcdb8a39fcce2/436db/_2748ab1763.webp 200w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 100px) 100px, 100vw"}]},"width":100,"height":140}}}}},{"slug":"czdxxs","title":"肠子的小心思","author":"[德] 朱莉娅•恩德斯","description":"德国图书界的黑马，口嫌体正直的德国人，一面对粑粑说着“不要不要”，一面看得好污好欢乐。原来，德国人觉得理所当然的马桶竟是痔疮的罪魁祸首；如此现代化的今天，蹲坑这种看似原始的行为竟然还在全世界一半以上的地区保留着，而且这才是大便的正确解锁方式；跟肠子相关的事，不仅有趣，还密切关系到人体的健康状况，一个感觉不好的肠道会让我们感到沮丧，而一个健康的、营养良好的肠道会大大地改善我们的情绪……谁能想到这些奇葩欢乐的内容，竟是一位软萌妹子所写，还一举俘获36个国家和地区读者的心。让我们跟着这本新鲜出炉带着屎味的书，一起开启神奇的消化道之旅吧。","rank":50,"published_at":"2022-01-17T07:39:36.000Z","image":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#f8f8f8","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/7259b6eccdab09b67d2c74610ca7b2b0/3212f/_69bb440905.jpg","srcSet":"/static/7259b6eccdab09b67d2c74610ca7b2b0/5c809/_69bb440905.jpg 25w,\n/static/7259b6eccdab09b67d2c74610ca7b2b0/5c9f3/_69bb440905.jpg 50w,\n/static/7259b6eccdab09b67d2c74610ca7b2b0/3212f/_69bb440905.jpg 100w,\n/static/7259b6eccdab09b67d2c74610ca7b2b0/291ee/_69bb440905.jpg 200w","sizes":"(min-width: 100px) 100px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/7259b6eccdab09b67d2c74610ca7b2b0/7f5c9/_69bb440905.webp 25w,\n/static/7259b6eccdab09b67d2c74610ca7b2b0/de8f1/_69bb440905.webp 50w,\n/static/7259b6eccdab09b67d2c74610ca7b2b0/fd5fd/_69bb440905.webp 100w,\n/static/7259b6eccdab09b67d2c74610ca7b2b0/436db/_69bb440905.webp 200w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 100px) 100px, 100vw"}]},"width":100,"height":140}}}}},{"slug":"huxihuaweikongqi","title":"当呼吸化为空气","author":"[美] 保罗·卡拉尼什","description":"全世界只有万分之零点一二的人会在36岁前患上肺癌，保罗·卡拉尼什（Paul Kalanithi）是其中之一。当你读到这本书时，他已经不在人世。保罗曾获得过美国斯坦福大学英语文学及人体生物学双料学位，并于英国剑桥大学获得科学史与哲学研究硕士学位，以优异成绩获得美国耶鲁大学医学博士学位，即将获得斯坦福医学院外科教授职位并主持自己的研究室。2013年，即将抵达人生巅峰的保罗，忽然被诊断出患有第四期肺癌。自此，他开始以医生和患者的双重身份，记录自己的余生，反思医疗与人性。他的文章刊登在《纽约时报》《华盛顿邮报》等媒体，获得了全球读者关注。本书文笔优美，诚挚感人，书里有着对人性、生死、医疗的深沉思索，让全球无数读者为之动容。\n","rank":50,"published_at":"2022-01-17T07:35:25.000Z","image":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#f8f8f8","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/ee3dd3317a3ec261286dda1aec6efdef/3212f/_8eecf4d795.jpg","srcSet":"/static/ee3dd3317a3ec261286dda1aec6efdef/5c809/_8eecf4d795.jpg 25w,\n/static/ee3dd3317a3ec261286dda1aec6efdef/5c9f3/_8eecf4d795.jpg 50w,\n/static/ee3dd3317a3ec261286dda1aec6efdef/3212f/_8eecf4d795.jpg 100w,\n/static/ee3dd3317a3ec261286dda1aec6efdef/291ee/_8eecf4d795.jpg 200w","sizes":"(min-width: 100px) 100px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/ee3dd3317a3ec261286dda1aec6efdef/7f5c9/_8eecf4d795.webp 25w,\n/static/ee3dd3317a3ec261286dda1aec6efdef/de8f1/_8eecf4d795.webp 50w,\n/static/ee3dd3317a3ec261286dda1aec6efdef/fd5fd/_8eecf4d795.webp 100w,\n/static/ee3dd3317a3ec261286dda1aec6efdef/436db/_8eecf4d795.webp 200w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 100px) 100px, 100vw"}]},"width":100,"height":140}}}}},{"slug":"womenweishenmeshengbing","title":"我们为什么生病","author":"[美] R.M.尼斯 / [美] G.C.威廉斯","description":"这是近50年来在生物医学领域里写的很重要的一本书……关于我们的身体为什么这样对创伤和疾病作出反应的有说服力的探索。大多数人都知道达尔文学说。但是现在，在开创一个新的考察进化论和医学的领域里。尼斯和威廉斯博士指出疾病的许多方面不过是进化过程的副作用。事实上，人类和他们的敌人——病毒、细菌和寄生虫之间不断的战争——确实是一场进化史中的军备竞赛，在这场竞赛中，我们人类需要利用关于自然选择的知识使我们永远处于领先地位。","rank":50,"published_at":"2022-01-17T07:31:34.000Z","image":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#e8e8e8","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/b67dc0e60d19a2a7c5fc02fcf3795040/3212f/_848decc194.jpg","srcSet":"/static/b67dc0e60d19a2a7c5fc02fcf3795040/5c809/_848decc194.jpg 25w,\n/static/b67dc0e60d19a2a7c5fc02fcf3795040/5c9f3/_848decc194.jpg 50w,\n/static/b67dc0e60d19a2a7c5fc02fcf3795040/3212f/_848decc194.jpg 100w,\n/static/b67dc0e60d19a2a7c5fc02fcf3795040/291ee/_848decc194.jpg 200w","sizes":"(min-width: 100px) 100px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/b67dc0e60d19a2a7c5fc02fcf3795040/7f5c9/_848decc194.webp 25w,\n/static/b67dc0e60d19a2a7c5fc02fcf3795040/de8f1/_848decc194.webp 50w,\n/static/b67dc0e60d19a2a7c5fc02fcf3795040/fd5fd/_848decc194.webp 100w,\n/static/b67dc0e60d19a2a7c5fc02fcf3795040/436db/_848decc194.webp 200w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 100px) 100px, 100vw"}]},"width":100,"height":140}}}}},{"slug":"aibola","title":"血疫（埃博拉的故事）","author":"[美] 理查德·普雷斯顿","description":"文明与病毒之间，只隔了一个航班的距离。\n\n来自热带雨林的危险病毒，可在24小时内乘飞机抵达地球上的任何城市。航空线路连接了全世界的所有城市，构成网络。\n\n埃博拉已经进入网络，开始环球旅行。\n\n卡尔•约翰逊，埃博拉病毒的发现者之一，他在病毒探索史上是个大人物，发现并命名了地球上好几种最危险的病原体。\n\n“大自然并不平静，我很高兴，”他这么说，“但在今天这样的日子里，咱们就当大自然很平静好了。所有怪物和猛兽都有平静的时刻。”\n\n“扎伊尔当时发生了什么？”我问。","rank":50,"published_at":"2022-01-17T07:08:38.000Z","image":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#e8e8f8","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/e528091c235826a90b94829de9979c96/3212f/_d24b8475fa.jpg","srcSet":"/static/e528091c235826a90b94829de9979c96/5c809/_d24b8475fa.jpg 25w,\n/static/e528091c235826a90b94829de9979c96/5c9f3/_d24b8475fa.jpg 50w,\n/static/e528091c235826a90b94829de9979c96/3212f/_d24b8475fa.jpg 100w,\n/static/e528091c235826a90b94829de9979c96/291ee/_d24b8475fa.jpg 200w","sizes":"(min-width: 100px) 100px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/e528091c235826a90b94829de9979c96/7f5c9/_d24b8475fa.webp 25w,\n/static/e528091c235826a90b94829de9979c96/de8f1/_d24b8475fa.webp 50w,\n/static/e528091c235826a90b94829de9979c96/fd5fd/_d24b8475fa.webp 100w,\n/static/e528091c235826a90b94829de9979c96/436db/_d24b8475fa.webp 200w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 100px) 100px, 100vw"}]},"width":100,"height":140}}}}},{"slug":"a-brief-history-of-humankind","title":"人类简史","author":"[以色列] 尤瓦尔·赫拉利","description":"尤瓦尔·赫拉利，1976年生，牛津大学历史学博士，现为耶路撒冷希伯来大学的历史系教授，青年怪才，全球瞩目的新锐历史学家，擅长世界历史和宏观历史进程研究，在学术领域和大众出版领域都有很大的兴趣。《人类简史》一书让他一举成名，成为以色列超级畅销书，目前这本书已授20多个国家版权，在历史学之外，人类学、生态学、基因学等领域的知识信手拈来。\n","rank":50,"published_at":"2022-01-03T08:13:41.000Z","image":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#d8d8d8","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/1c1e53528ded0ffcd368a7c3b6cea847/3212f/_2a5eb5bbba.jpg","srcSet":"/static/1c1e53528ded0ffcd368a7c3b6cea847/5c809/_2a5eb5bbba.jpg 25w,\n/static/1c1e53528ded0ffcd368a7c3b6cea847/5c9f3/_2a5eb5bbba.jpg 50w,\n/static/1c1e53528ded0ffcd368a7c3b6cea847/3212f/_2a5eb5bbba.jpg 100w,\n/static/1c1e53528ded0ffcd368a7c3b6cea847/291ee/_2a5eb5bbba.jpg 200w","sizes":"(min-width: 100px) 100px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/1c1e53528ded0ffcd368a7c3b6cea847/7f5c9/_2a5eb5bbba.webp 25w,\n/static/1c1e53528ded0ffcd368a7c3b6cea847/de8f1/_2a5eb5bbba.webp 50w,\n/static/1c1e53528ded0ffcd368a7c3b6cea847/fd5fd/_2a5eb5bbba.webp 100w,\n/static/1c1e53528ded0ffcd368a7c3b6cea847/436db/_2a5eb5bbba.webp 200w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 100px) 100px, 100vw"}]},"width":100,"height":140}}}}},{"slug":"bnlfmxs","title":"别闹了，费曼先生","author":"[美] 理查德·费曼","description":"费曼得过诺贝尔奖，是现代最伟大的理论物理学家之一。但他同时也可能是历史上唯一被按摩院请去画裸体画、偷偷打开放着原子弹机密文件的保险箱，在巴西桑巴乐团担任鼓手的科学家。他曾跟爱因斯坦和波尔等大师讨论物理问题，也曾在赌城跟职业赌徒研究输赢机率。\n","rank":50,"published_at":"2022-01-16T04:31:40.000Z","image":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#f8f8f8","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/7e5a2d290d6dd88cd9fd47725c524471/3212f/_6fadc4785b.jpg","srcSet":"/static/7e5a2d290d6dd88cd9fd47725c524471/5c809/_6fadc4785b.jpg 25w,\n/static/7e5a2d290d6dd88cd9fd47725c524471/5c9f3/_6fadc4785b.jpg 50w,\n/static/7e5a2d290d6dd88cd9fd47725c524471/3212f/_6fadc4785b.jpg 100w,\n/static/7e5a2d290d6dd88cd9fd47725c524471/291ee/_6fadc4785b.jpg 200w","sizes":"(min-width: 100px) 100px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/7e5a2d290d6dd88cd9fd47725c524471/7f5c9/_6fadc4785b.webp 25w,\n/static/7e5a2d290d6dd88cd9fd47725c524471/de8f1/_6fadc4785b.webp 50w,\n/static/7e5a2d290d6dd88cd9fd47725c524471/fd5fd/_6fadc4785b.webp 100w,\n/static/7e5a2d290d6dd88cd9fd47725c524471/436db/_6fadc4785b.webp 200w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 100px) 100px, 100vw"}]},"width":100,"height":140}}}}},{"slug":"a-brief-history-of-time","title":"时间简史","author":"[英] 史蒂芬·霍金|","description":"《时间简史》讲述是探索时间和空间核心秘密的故事，是关于宇宙本性的最前沿知识，包括我们的宇宙图像、空间和时间、膨胀的宇宙不确定性原理、基本粒子和自然的力、黑洞、黑洞不是这么黑、时间箭头等内容。第一版中的许多理论预言，后来在对微观或宏观宇宙世界观测中得到证实。\n\n自1988年首版以来，《时间简史》已成为全球科学著作的里程碑。它被翻译成40种文字，销售了近1000万册。此版更新了内容，把许多观测揭示的新知识，以及霍金最新的研究纳入，并配以250幅照片和电脑制作的三维和四维空间图。","rank":50,"published_at":"2022-01-15T16:41:29.000Z","image":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#181818","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/40b9dbb981c64705bd94c1adc4f4bd02/3212f/_28c578e85d.jpg","srcSet":"/static/40b9dbb981c64705bd94c1adc4f4bd02/5c809/_28c578e85d.jpg 25w,\n/static/40b9dbb981c64705bd94c1adc4f4bd02/5c9f3/_28c578e85d.jpg 50w,\n/static/40b9dbb981c64705bd94c1adc4f4bd02/3212f/_28c578e85d.jpg 100w,\n/static/40b9dbb981c64705bd94c1adc4f4bd02/291ee/_28c578e85d.jpg 200w","sizes":"(min-width: 100px) 100px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/40b9dbb981c64705bd94c1adc4f4bd02/7f5c9/_28c578e85d.webp 25w,\n/static/40b9dbb981c64705bd94c1adc4f4bd02/de8f1/_28c578e85d.webp 50w,\n/static/40b9dbb981c64705bd94c1adc4f4bd02/fd5fd/_28c578e85d.webp 100w,\n/static/40b9dbb981c64705bd94c1adc4f4bd02/436db/_28c578e85d.webp 200w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 100px) 100px, 100vw"}]},"width":100,"height":140}}}}},{"slug":"zhdgb","title":"最好的告别","author":"[美] 阿图·葛文德","description":"当独立、自助的生活不能再维持时，我们该怎么办？在生命临近终点的时刻，我们该和医生谈些什么？应该如何优雅地跨越生命的终点？对于这些问题，大多数人缺少清晰的观念，而只是把命运交由医学、技术和陌生人来掌控。影响世界的医生阿图•葛文德结合其多年的外科医生经验与流畅的文笔，讲述了一个个伤感而发人深省的故事，对在21世纪变老意味着什么进行了清醒、深入的探索。本书富有洞见、感人至深，并为我们提供了实用的路线图，告诉我们为了使生命最后的岁月有意义，我们可以做什么、应该做什么。","rank":50,"published_at":"2022-01-15T16:13:07.000Z","image":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#f8e8c8","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/336bc91ec3ed830cd6b0cbe34672e3e4/3212f/_3e1077dc99.jpg","srcSet":"/static/336bc91ec3ed830cd6b0cbe34672e3e4/5c809/_3e1077dc99.jpg 25w,\n/static/336bc91ec3ed830cd6b0cbe34672e3e4/5c9f3/_3e1077dc99.jpg 50w,\n/static/336bc91ec3ed830cd6b0cbe34672e3e4/3212f/_3e1077dc99.jpg 100w,\n/static/336bc91ec3ed830cd6b0cbe34672e3e4/291ee/_3e1077dc99.jpg 200w","sizes":"(min-width: 100px) 100px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/336bc91ec3ed830cd6b0cbe34672e3e4/7f5c9/_3e1077dc99.webp 25w,\n/static/336bc91ec3ed830cd6b0cbe34672e3e4/de8f1/_3e1077dc99.webp 50w,\n/static/336bc91ec3ed830cd6b0cbe34672e3e4/fd5fd/_3e1077dc99.webp 100w,\n/static/336bc91ec3ed830cd6b0cbe34672e3e4/436db/_3e1077dc99.webp 200w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 100px) 100px, 100vw"}]},"width":100,"height":140}}}}},{"slug":"cydwqd","title":"从一到无穷大","author":"[美] 乔治·伽莫夫","description":"本书是最负盛名的世界科普经典著作之一，它曾引领千千万万的读者进入科学世界。许多人都是因为在十几岁的时候读到这本书，才第一次真正领略了科学的奇迹和奥秘。作者以其幽默的笔调和高超的教学技巧，探讨了宏观世界和微观世界、数论、空间和时间的相对性、熵、基因、原子结构、核裂变和太阳系的起源等主题。无论你的科学知识水平如何，你都会从这本不同寻常的书中获得许多乐趣和激励。它是任何对科学世界充满好奇的人的必读书。","rank":50,"published_at":"2022-01-15T16:02:30.000Z","image":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#386888","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/164bb4c33b06c7c0086dbe8b6e36c5b8/3212f/_101a1972df.jpg","srcSet":"/static/164bb4c33b06c7c0086dbe8b6e36c5b8/5c809/_101a1972df.jpg 25w,\n/static/164bb4c33b06c7c0086dbe8b6e36c5b8/5c9f3/_101a1972df.jpg 50w,\n/static/164bb4c33b06c7c0086dbe8b6e36c5b8/3212f/_101a1972df.jpg 100w,\n/static/164bb4c33b06c7c0086dbe8b6e36c5b8/291ee/_101a1972df.jpg 200w","sizes":"(min-width: 100px) 100px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/164bb4c33b06c7c0086dbe8b6e36c5b8/7f5c9/_101a1972df.webp 25w,\n/static/164bb4c33b06c7c0086dbe8b6e36c5b8/de8f1/_101a1972df.webp 50w,\n/static/164bb4c33b06c7c0086dbe8b6e36c5b8/fd5fd/_101a1972df.webp 100w,\n/static/164bb4c33b06c7c0086dbe8b6e36c5b8/436db/_101a1972df.webp 200w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 100px) 100px, 100vw"}]},"width":100,"height":140}}}}},{"slug":"sdztzm","title":"上帝掷骰子吗","author":"曹天元","description":"这本书是关于量子论的故事。量子论是一个极为奇妙的理论：从物理角度来说，它在科学家中间引起了最为激烈的争议和关注；从现实角度来说，它给我们的社会带来了无与伦比的变化和进步；从科学史角度来说，也几乎没有哪段历史比量子论的创立得到了更为彻底的研究。然而不可思议的是，它的基本观点和假说至今没有渗透到大众的意识中去，这无疑又给它增添了一道神秘的光环。","rank":50,"published_at":"2022-01-15T15:46:14.000Z","image":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#080808","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/947c77ec2bfe4056d42e7b9838e3bafb/3212f/_024ff6ec09.jpg","srcSet":"/static/947c77ec2bfe4056d42e7b9838e3bafb/5c809/_024ff6ec09.jpg 25w,\n/static/947c77ec2bfe4056d42e7b9838e3bafb/5c9f3/_024ff6ec09.jpg 50w,\n/static/947c77ec2bfe4056d42e7b9838e3bafb/3212f/_024ff6ec09.jpg 100w,\n/static/947c77ec2bfe4056d42e7b9838e3bafb/291ee/_024ff6ec09.jpg 200w","sizes":"(min-width: 100px) 100px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/947c77ec2bfe4056d42e7b9838e3bafb/7f5c9/_024ff6ec09.webp 25w,\n/static/947c77ec2bfe4056d42e7b9838e3bafb/de8f1/_024ff6ec09.webp 50w,\n/static/947c77ec2bfe4056d42e7b9838e3bafb/fd5fd/_024ff6ec09.webp 100w,\n/static/947c77ec2bfe4056d42e7b9838e3bafb/436db/_024ff6ec09.webp 200w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 100px) 100px, 100vw"}]},"width":100,"height":140}}}}}]},"strapiBookTags":{"name":"科普","slug":"science"},"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"收集优质资源","author":"@learn-anything.cn","description":"追求极简语言，说明事物因果！","email":"lh@learn-anything.cn"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"science","pageSize":24,"total":20,"numPages":1,"currentPage":1,"skip":0}},
